{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/toge-productions-borong-penghargaan-video-game-tingkat-asia-tenggara/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Toge Productions Borong Penghargaan Video Game Tingkat Asia Tenggara","content":"<p dir=\"ltr\">Kuala Lumpur, 8 November 2017 &#8211; Studio pengembang dan penerbit <i>game</i> asal Tangerang, Toge Productions, minggu ini pulang ke Indonesia dengan bangga sambil memboyong sejumlah penghargaan dari ajang SEA Games Award yang dianugerahkan di Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia. Penghargaan bergengsi tingkat regional ini diberikan bersamaan dengan berlangsungnya Level Up KL 2017. Rentetan acara dengan fokus pada industri <i>game</i> regional dan global yang diadakan oleh Malaysia Digital Economy Corporation (MDEC).</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Penghargaan yang diterima antara lain adalah:</p>\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\">Best Visual Art Award (penghargaan untuk visual terbaik) &#8211; My Lovely Daughter</h4>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_26513\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-26513\" data-attachment-id=\"26513\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/toge-productions-borong-penghargaan-video-game-tingkat-asia-tenggara/attachment/isi-1-7-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-1-7-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"My Lovely Daughter (Sumber: Toge Productions)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;My Lovely Daughter (Sumber: Toge Productions)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-1-7-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-1-7-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-26513\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-1-7-1.jpg\" alt=\"My Lovely Daughter (Sumber: Toge Productions)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-26513\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">My Lovely Daughter (Sumber: Toge Productions)</p></div></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><i>My Lovely Daughter</i> merupakan <i>game</i> yang dikembangkan oleh GameChanger Studio asal Tangerang, dengan Toge Productions berperan sebagai penerbit. <i>Game</i> simulasi dengan tema fantasi yang sangat gelap ini bercerita tentang seorang ayah yang ingin menghidupkan kembali anaknya, meskipun cara yang ia lakukan amat sangat kontroversial dan penuh dengan nilai moral yang perlu dipertanyakan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_26498\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-26498\" data-attachment-id=\"26498\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/toge-productions-borong-penghargaan-video-game-tingkat-asia-tenggara/attachment/isi-6-4-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-6-4-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sea Games Award.\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sea Games Award. &lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-6-4-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-6-4-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-26498\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-6-4-1.jpg\" alt=\"Sea Games Award. (Sumber: Toge Productions)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-26498\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sea Games Award.</p></div></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Arahan visual yang diusung oleh <i>My Lovely Daughter</i> tampak seperti coret-coretan yang biasa ditemukan di jurnal-jurnal zaman dahulu, dipadu inspirasi dari komik horor dan pemilihan warna yang disesuaikan dengan tema serta latar belakang waktu dan tempat dalam <i>game</i>.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><i>My Lovely Daughter</i> terpilih sebagai pemenang mengalahkan nominasi lain yaitu <i>Postknight</i> buatan Kurechii Studio asal Malaysia dan <i>She and the Light Bearer</i> buatan Mojiken Studio asal Surabaya, Indonesia yang juga diterbitkan oleh Toge Productions.</p>\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\">Best Gameplay Award (penghargaan untuk <i>gameplay </i>terbaik) &#8211; <i>Infectonator 3: Apocalypse</i></h4>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_26510\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-26510\" data-attachment-id=\"26510\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/toge-productions-borong-penghargaan-video-game-tingkat-asia-tenggara/attachment/isi-2-5-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-2-5-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Infectonator 3 (Sumber: Toge Productions)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Infectonator 3 (Sumber: Toge Productions)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-2-5-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-2-5-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-26510\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-2-5-1.jpg\" alt=\"Infectonator 3 (Sumber: Toge Productions)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-26510\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Infectonator 3 (Sumber: Toge Productions)</p></div></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Gameplay adalah istilah yang digunakan untuk menjelaskan aturan atau cara bermain suatu <i>game</i>. Untuk penghargaan ini, Toge Productions sukses menyabet kehormatan dengan <i>game</i> buatan divisi pengembang internal mereka sendiri, yaitu <i>Infectonator 3: Apocalypse</i>. <i>Infectonator </i>sendiri merupakan seri <i>game </i>andalan Toge Productions yang sebelumnya telah memenangkan beberapa penghargaan <i>video game</i> baik untuk tingkat lokal, regional, maupun global.</p>\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\">Grand Jury Award &#8211; <i>Infectonator 3: Apocalypse</i></h4>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_26507\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-26507\" data-attachment-id=\"26507\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/toge-productions-borong-penghargaan-video-game-tingkat-asia-tenggara/attachment/isi-3-5-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-3-5-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Infectonator 3 (Sumber: Toge Productions)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Infectonator 3 (Sumber: Toge Productions)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-3-5-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-3-5-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-26507\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-3-5-1.jpg\" alt=\"Infectonator 3 (Sumber: Toge Productions)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-26507\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Infectonator 3 (Sumber: Toge Productions)</p></div></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Penghargaan terakhir yang diterima adalah penghargaan tertinggi yang diberikan para juri di ajang SEA Games Award, yaitu Grand Jury Award. Kehormatan besar ini diterima oleh <i>Infectonator 3: Apocalypse</i>. Sebagai penghargaan tertinggi, Grand Jury Award dinilai dari hasil produk <i>game </i>secara keseluruhan, baik itu <i>gameplay</i>, visual, dan sebagainya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_26501\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-26501\" data-attachment-id=\"26501\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/toge-productions-borong-penghargaan-video-game-tingkat-asia-tenggara/attachment/isi-5-6-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-5-6-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Winner of Grand Jury Award.\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Winner of Grand Jury Award. &lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-5-6-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-5-6-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-26501\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-5-6-1.jpg\" alt=\"Winner of Grand Jury Award. \" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-26501\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Winner of Grand Jury Award.</p></div></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Selain tiga penghargaan tersebut, Toge Productions juga mendapatkan kehormatan untuk masuk beberapa nominasi lain seperti Best Storytelling Award (penyampaian cerita terbaik) untuk <i>My Lovely Daughter </i>dan <i>She and the Light Bearer</i>, serta Best Audio Award (audio terbaik) untuk <i>She and the Light Bearer</i>.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">“Selain bangga dengan penghargaan yang kami terima, kami harap developer <i>game </i>Indonesia lainnya bisa terinspirasi untuk berkarya lebih baik dan giat lagi, karena di era globalisasi seperti sekarang ini, bersaing dengan developer lain dari mancanegara bukanlah hal yang mustahil untuk dilakukan,” ujar Kris Antoni selaku CEO dari Toge Productions.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_26504\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-26504\" data-attachment-id=\"26504\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/toge-productions-borong-penghargaan-video-game-tingkat-asia-tenggara/attachment/isi-4-6-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-4-6-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Logo Toge Productions (Sumber: Toge Productions)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Logo Toge Productions (Sumber: Toge Productions)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-4-6-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-4-6-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-26504\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-4-6-1.jpg\" alt=\"Logo Toge Productions (Sumber: Toge Productions)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-26504\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Logo Toge Productions (Sumber: Toge Productions)</p></div></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Setelah sukses di acara Level Up KL 2017, selanjutnya Toge Productions juga akan membawa karya mereka ke acara <i>game </i>terbesar di Korea Selatan, G-STAR 2017, yang berlangsung di Kota Busan dari 14 November 2017 sampai 19 November 2017.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"01a94880-cffa-5c73-9555-665cbf7b60cb"}}}